{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1fbbee7dd5","title":"毛泽东关于区域自治问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6bd2a562a7","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7235338242","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于区域自治问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"},{"id":"49313d2469","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"},{"id":"dd2b4836d2","type":"appellation","text":"刘、周、朱、任、李维汉同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"},{"id":"51c25c454b","type":"paragraph","text":"区域自治问题，牵涉很广，有西藏、青海、宁夏、新疆、甘肃、西康、云南、广西、贵州、海南、湘西等处，有的须成立内蒙那样的大区域政府，有的须成立包括几个县的小区域政府，有的是一个县或一个区的政府，疆域划分，人员配备，政策指导，问题甚多，须加统筹。此电所称东藏自治区域，是与西康省政府并立的，还是属于西康之内的？其疆域如何？是否事前得到中央批准？请维汉查告，或去电询问。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"},{"id":"8998662331","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5"}],"page":{"id":"8f94e82342","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1fbbee7dd5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}